imdb.plot outline: Comedians Marc Yaffee and Adam Stone's travels lead them to encounters with the culture and traditions of Indigenous inhabitants while crossing America's trails - up to Alaska and across the seas to Hawaii. Our two traveling comedians work the Tribal Casino Comedy circuit, crisscrossing the country. Each Casino stop generates a new adventure where Marc and Adam interact with tribal members, sample foods, participate in cultural activities and visit the notable landmarks. From canoe journeys and wild horse racing to Powwows and stick games tournaments, these entertaining adventures provide insight and knowledge.
